profile:
Finesse Concrete Project is a versatile construction services company - offering a wide range of solutions for client projects from home-owners to larger scale undertakings. Although starting out in primarily concrete, and specializing within this niche, FCP provides stable, long-lasting solutions to any number of commercial and non-commercial designs. 

Our clients have included many homeowners across the GTA, from Oakville to Downtown Toronto. Construction industry veterans such as PCL, as well as a number of other residential construction companies such as Mattamy Homes and Bomanite are also familiar names to us, as we've worked side by side on many an occasion.

Based in the Greater Toronto Area, we are able to service a variety of residential requirements. Ask us about our luxury offerings as well - we bring an artisanal and highly detail oriented approach in order to meet high level client demands as needed. With our discretion and care, you will hardly know we were there.
services:
Concrete - we bring a detailed, experienced perspective to all our client needs, and complete your projects with a great deal of time and cost-efficiency.



Demolition & Clean-up - Knowledge of careful and considered demolition, as well as clean-up of a work site is something we consider as important as the construction itself. 


Epoxy design - Make your home truly your own, with our custom made epoxy. Designed by you and completed by us, this unique offering will display the bespoke nature of your home - and set you apart from other homeowners. 


Wood work and design - Through the years our knowledge of wood working and design has lead to being able to offer a truly versatile service. We can offer the ability to design and execute on any number of foundational, functional and decorative designs.

Atrium Design Construction Ltd is a one-stop full-service contractor for any home renovation or new construction. We are recognized for our ability to work under the small access properties in Downtown Toronto and also experienced dealing with big projects in the outskirts of the city.

Atrium Design Construction Ltd was founded by Carlos Salgado, an interior designer and veteran renovator with experience working in Miami Florida homes for 10 years and in Toronto homes for another 15 years. We carry all the equipment and all the sub-trades necessary for any job. We have associates and subcontractors who assist us in making sure your project is done correctly, following regulation, safely and on budget.

We like to recommend the best products to the clients. We understand that every project is different with different budgets and expectations. We take care of homes as if they were our own. The finished product has to be perfect, every time.

specialities:
The Atrium way
The client has a desire to renovate part of his house and reaches out to us.
We translate the client's idea into an actionable work order, including estimates, itineraries, city permits and a list of all trades to be employed in the project.
We take care of all the trades ourselves with our in house professional personnel and our affiliate trades. We work along with licensed electricians, qualified machine operators, experienced handy men, among others. (We usually do 90% of the work ourselves, the other 10% is done by specialty trades which we deal with directly).
We take the client through the exciting journey of a home renovation. We explain the process as it unfolds day by day.
We make sure the project is finished with the upmost level of excellence, on time and in budget. We aren't satisfied until the client is satisfied.

profile:
Who we are…
ACA Advanced Contracting provides services of renovating homes and commercial property. We are in the business to transform the client’s premises into a place worth living or conducting business with our luxuriously stylish design. 
Our Expertise and Core Values 
We make use of our construction and architecture knowledge, organizational resources and passion to manage the project from start to finish using project management tools and techniques. However, big or small the project is, we have the ability and capability to meet our clients’ expectations in line with our core value of respect for their business and family because we understand how obtrusive it can be, to disrupt the daily routine – especially with children and pets around.
How do we Operate? 
Like any properly run project, it all starts with a conversation.  We will set up an initial meeting to discuss at length the scope of work involved and share our ideas to make their premises par excellence by providing cost-effective solutions exceeding their expectations, remaining within the constraints of their budget. 
Once the terms and conditions are agreed and we receive their signal to go ahead, we start the planning process. We know that little things do count – that’s why we provide our clients with a detailed estimate or quote listing the major components of the project, along with an estimated timeline of the entire project including the contingency buffer. 
Since we are flexible and accommodating, so as the project progresses, our clients can expect regular updates from us and we have a set procedure for Change Management to avoid conflicts. 
Our Clients’ Expectations
Safety of human life and property is our top priority and as such, at the end of every day when we are done with working at their homes or businesses, they can expect the project site to be clean, tidy and safe.  It is also imperative to inform you that ACA Advanced Contracting is fully insured and WSIB compliant.
ACA Advanced Contracting looks forward to having a lasting business relationship with our clients with respect and integrity at the core of our heart, as we care about our Client.

With our personalized customer service and reasonable pricing, we are tough competitor to beat.
  
As a General Contractor we provide an immense amount of services, mainly focusing within the exterior and interior of residential and commercial construction. Specializing in complete renovations, new construction, structural work as well as additions. This includes but not limiting to, kitchens, bathrooms, basements, garages and Customized Murals & Decoractive Painting.
At Protek Construction Inc. you can expect our service to be professional and reliable with the sincerity and friendliness of a small family business.
Please feel free to browse our website, if you have any questions or are interested in a free quote, please call 647-209 -1411.
